text: Yoshihide Fukutome is a former modern pentathlete from Japan. Yoshihide competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics. He was born on March 10, 1933 and died on January 5, 2022.Yoshihide Fukutome == References == Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Olympians for Japan Category:Japanese modern pentathletes
